{"tid":1656961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰俘］香港內戰狀態，被捕手足係戰俘","createTime":"2019-10-16T00:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T01:08:07.000Z","uid":62805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30ea644e5a76283c3be8f8c3ac43ba2da6cbcac3","tid":1656961,"uid":62805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:41:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60157048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60157048&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=6a5740c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60157048&h=c69126c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60157048</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其中16歲男學生的代表大律師庭外表示，男學生被捕後，有警員在警署拿出預備好的歌詞，迫他唱《願榮光歸警察》，遭男學生拒絕。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果香港當前狀況係內戰，手足就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戰俘</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n大家用戰俘呢隻字點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4d4b4ec00a96a40abd11772ef65acc6b60ada4","tid":1656961,"uid":195166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"戰俘都受日內瓦公約保護<br />\n<br />\n第二條　戰俘是在敵方國家的權力下，而不是在俘獲戰俘的個人或隊伍的權力下。<br />\n<br />\n他們應在任何時候都應受到人道待遇和保護，特別是不遭受暴行、侮辱和公眾好奇心的煩擾。 對戰俘的報復措施應予禁止。<br />\n<br />\n第三條　戰俘應享受人身及榮譽之尊重。對於婦女的待遇應充分顧及其性別。<br />\n<br />\n黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9130c004bdc60b04ee5076d9db5de78ecf0dc11f","tid":1656961,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:05:04.000Z","msg":"內戰多數比主權國家既戰爭殘酷<br />\n因為好多公約都唔適用"},{"pid":"8816b6f80cca27a30b9b6ecc7bf802220c3b2156","tid":1656961,"uid":287433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:07:47.000Z","msg":"預備好的歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,佢地仲有時間作曲"},{"pid":"04adaa6b41444d7e4193e829673815227e3f7ee0","tid":1656961,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:07:56.000Z","msg":"顛撚左"},{"pid":"b4e50db3f8c31c38e8ec518176b3aa3f0cd971ca","tid":1656961,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:08:07.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n辛苦製作，求手足幫推！！！"}]}